<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240612/1718166970226045733.png" title="1718166970226045733.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-06-12 123502.png"/></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">为进一步推动党纪学习教育的深入开展，积极引导全体党员在学纪、知纪、明纪、守纪中走在前、作表率，增强全体党员的纪律意识和规矩意识。5月27日经济管理学院学生党支部书记熊奕俊以《</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">争做守纪律，讲规矩的表率》为题，为经济管理学院学生党支部全体党员上了一堂生动的专题党课。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240612/1718167031815067240.png" title="1718167031815067240.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-06-12 123508.png" width="791" height="460" style="width: 791px; height: 460px;"/></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 1.5px;">本次党课，熊奕俊书记主要从以下三个方面进行讲授：一是坚定理想信念，强化学习；</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; text-align: justify; caret-color: red; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-indent: 2.21428em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">二是强化政治素养，严于律己；三是确保对党忠诚，强化监督管理。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 0px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240612/1718167107160035100.png" title="1718167107160035100.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-06-12 123516.png" width="786" height="581" style="width: 786px; height: 581px;"/></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px;">在授课过程中，熊奕俊书记指出，</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 32px; caret-color: red;">我们要时刻牢记自己的身份和职责，不断提高自己的政治觉悟和思想认识。</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; caret-color: red;">要从思想上筑牢防线，从行动上严格自律，时刻警醒自己，以实际行动维护党的形象和威信。</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2.21428em; caret-color: red;">同时，必须严于律己、以身作则、防微杜渐，做到“四慎”——</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2.21428em; caret-color: red;">慎独、</span><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2.21428em; caret-color: red;">慎微、慎权、慎友。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); caret-color: red; letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">通过此次党纪学习教育专题党课，全体学生党员表示将不忘初心，进一步强化纪律意识、加强自我约束、提高免疫能力，争做守纪律、讲规矩、忠诚干净担当的表率。</span></p>